{"tid":1861231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「學車」教車師傅 究竟係我問題定佢問題？","createTime":"2020-02-04T04:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T09:14:45.000Z","uid":274954,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"a9efef9d94b3e56609330a9b54b9a29affe53b0c","tid":1861231,"uid":274954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"學車都係想有個盡責d既師傅姐 ～<br />\n一開始佢直頭唔記得叫我上堂 <br />\n考完筆試 佢話會主動搵我約上堂 但一直等到12月尾佢都未搵我（3月頭考） 我都算啦 咁我主動搵佢去學車 我明白會唔記得 但佢就唔好應承人啦<br />\n啱啱完左新年假期 我都見佢未搵我 咁我緊張好正常姐 唯有又係我主動搵佢約上堂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zo5uwrP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzo5uwrP.png&h=a5e1e3a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgyWVTv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgyWVTv.png&h=494f1a88&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8X2ddFc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8X2ddFc.png&h=d0da36a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真心無信心合格到🤦🏻&zwj;♂️ 究竟係咪我太緊張？"},{"pid":"f0b06d0ffd1dcca387b790160fcdf4692a665060","tid":1861231,"uid":146620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"我上年十月中考 九月頭先開始學<br />\n然後最後係迫埋最後三星期學20堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係10日 最後pass左"},{"pid":"99cada5e2489cd2520539d59d444ee2e52a63ba5","tid":1861231,"uid":119250,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:57:52.000Z","msg":"遮啲唔遮啲 鏗鏘李安健"},{"pid":"c461209982a26bc8fceea0b909a9305c1af96fa8","tid":1861231,"uid":274954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0b06d0ffd1dcca387b790160fcdf4692a665060","tid":1861231,"uid":146620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"我上年十月中考 九月頭先開始學<br />\n然後最後係迫埋最後三星期學20堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係10日 最後pass左"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"好事定唔好事？"},{"pid"